# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the philippine department of justice -lrb- doj -rrb- said sunday that it is ready to file charges and prosecute the people uncovered to be behind the coup attempt of the rogue officers of the armed forces of the philippines -lrb- afp -rrb- as president arroyo declared a state of rebellion .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Department"
                  :op2 "of"
                  :op3 "Justice")
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Philippines")))
      :ARG1 (r / ready-02
            :ARG1 g
            :ARG2 (a / and
                  :op1 (f / file-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (c2 / charge-05))
                  :op2 (p / prosecute-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :ARG1-of (u / uncover-01
                                    :purpose (a2 / attempt-01
                                          :ARG0 (p3 / person
                                                :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                                      :ARG1 (f2 / force
                                                            :ARG1-of (a3 / arm-01)
                                                            :poss c)
                                                      :ARG2 (o / officer))
                                                :mod (r2 / rogue))
                                          :ARG1 (c3 / coup-01
                                                :ARG0 p3))))))
            :time (d / declare-01
                  :ARG0 (p4 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Arroyo")
                        :ARG0-of h
                        :ARG2 (p5 / president)))
            :ARG1 (s2 / state
                  :mod (r3 / rebel-01)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s3 / sunday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the german chemicals and pharmaceuticals giant bayer said friday it would sell its rhein chemie <unk> unit to a group of investors advised by the us firm advent international for ### million euros -lrb- ###.# million dollars -rrb- , including debt .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Bayer")
            :mod (g / giant)
            :mod (c2 / chemical)
            :mod (p / pharmaceutical)
            :mod (c3 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Germany")))
      :ARG1 (s2 / sell-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (u / unit
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Rhein"
                        :op2 "Chemie")
                  :poss c)
            :ARG2 (g2 / group
                  :consist-of (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (ii / invest-01)
                        :ARG1-of (a / advise-01
                              :ARG0 (f / firm
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 " advent"
                                          :op2 "International")
                                    :mod (c4 / country
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "United"
                                                :op2 "States"))))))
            :ARG3 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000
                  :unit (e / euro)
                  :ARG2-of (ii2 / include-01
                        :ARG1 (d / debt))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "State"
                  :op2 "Department")
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "US")))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (r / review-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (c2 / criticize-01
                        :ARG1 (m / media
                              :mod (p / political-party
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Greek")))
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / sharp-02)
                        :ARG1-of (c3 / contain-01
                              :ARG0 (d / document
                                    :ARG1-of (r2 / release-01
                                          :ARG0 g
                                          :time (w / week
                                                :mod (t / this)))))))
            :op2 (a2 / amend-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 c2
                  :ARG1-of (p2 / possible-01))
            :ARG1-of (f / follow-01
                  :ARG2 (c4 / complain-01
                        :ARG1-of (l / lodge-03
                              :location (a3 / and
                                    :op1 (h / here)
                                    :op2 (c5 / city
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "Athens")))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))
